OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,FThe first minister has said he will
OL,7,Fwelcome the support of any other
OL,8,Fpolitical party in delivering the
OL,9,FWelsh Government's spending plans.
OL,11,FDuring FMQs, Rhun ap Iorwerth was
OL,12,Fchallenged by the opposition leader,
OL,13,FReform UK's Dan Thomas, to say whether
OL,14,Fhe would work with his party. This is
OL,15,Fdespite the Plaid Cymru leader ruling
OL,16,Fthis out during the recent Senedd
OL,17,FElection campaign.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
