OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782906493
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,FIn response, the first minister said
OL,7,Fhe had met each of the other leaders,
OL,8,Fincluding Mr Thomas, for introductory
OL,9,Ftalks.
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru became the largest party
OL,12,Fin the Senedd after May's election,
OL,13,Fenough to form a government but not
OL,14,Fenough for an outright majority. This
OL,15,Fmeans it will need the support of
OL,16,Fother parties in order to pass key
OL,17,Flegislation and budgets.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
