CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782906493
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,FThe first minister said: "We recognise
OL,7,Fthis as a minority government, and
OL,8,Fthat is why when we appeal in the
OL,9,FSenedd for people, members here to
OL,10,Fsupport those measures to stabilise
OL,11,Fand get to grips with and bring down
OL,12,Fwaiting lists in the NHS.
OL,14,F"I would hope that that is something
OL,15,Fthat the member would be able to to
OL,16,Fsupport when I look at the measures
OL,17,Fbeing taken now to support families
OL,18,Fwith the cost of living crisis through
OL,19,Fexpanded childcare.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782906493
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,F"I'm hoping that this is something
OL,7,Fthat can appeal to members across this
OL,8,FSenedd - measures to improve school
OL,9,Fbuildings, and so on. This isn't a
OL,10,Fgovernment that doesn't recognise the
OL,11,Fneed to speak across this chamber.
OL,13,F"This is a government that's
OL,14,Fdetermined to put in place the program
OL,15,Fon which we stood and which we know we
OL,16,Fwill need the support of others to
OL,17,Fimplement."
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@KO]
