OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,FIn response, the Reform leader said:
OL,7,F"it's encouraging that the first
OL,8,Fminister seems to have changed his
OL,9,Fmind about working with Reform,
OL,10,Fbecause during the election you said
OL,11,Fyou wouldn't work with us, so that is
OL,12,Fa welcome U-turn.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
