CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782906493
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,F"Our red lines, though, would be to
OL,7,Fguarantee all student nurses and
OL,8,Fmidwives a job, that would be a red
OL,9,Fline for us when they finish their
OL,10,Ftraining. We would also want to
OL,11,Fincrease spending on children with
OL,12,Fadditional earning needs, and we want
OL,13,Fto stop spending taxpayers' money
OL,14,Fabroad and invest that money on Welsh
OL,15,FNHS and Welsh children. Those are our
OL,16,Fred lines."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@KO]
