PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782906493
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,FRed lines or otherwise, the exchange
OL,7,Freveals the precarious situation Plaid
OL,8,FCymru finds itself in. It's by far the
OL,9,Flargest party in the Senedd and no
OL,10,Fother parties are questioning its
OL,11,Fmandate, but they are repeatedly
OL,12,Freminding Rhun ap Iorwerth that he
OL,13,Fleads a minority government.
OL,15,FIn vote after vote, Plaid Cymru is
OL,16,Fhaving to try to reach some kind of
OL,17,Fagreement or face defeat and while the
OL,18,FFirst Minister talks about reaching
OL,19,Fout to other parties, the reality is
OL,20,Fthat none of the options are easy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782906493
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,FThere are only two Green MSs and one
OL,7,FLib Dem, not enough to reach a
OL,8,Fmajority. Labour is the most likely
OL,9,Fpartner but has signalled that it
OL,10,Fwon't be easily won over. The
OL,11,FConservatives did help Plaid Cymru out
OL,12,Fin a recent vote on childcare but have
OL,13,Fmade it clear that will be an
OL,14,Fexception.
OL,16,FIn this current situation, a senior
OL,17,FConservative source told me there are
OL,18,Fabsolutely no discussions going on
OL,19,Fwith the government about the
OL,20,Fsupplementary budget and that the Tory
OL,21,Fgroup won't be supporting it.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,433,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1782906493
OL,3,CFirst Minister welcomes support from
OL,4,Cany party on Plaid's spending plans
OL,6,FAnd the 'talks' referred to with
OL,7,FReform UK aren't exactly the beginning
OL,8,Fof a new friendship. Dan Thomas told
OL,9,Fthe chamber that the "introductory
OL,10,Fmeeting" avoided any policy discussion.
OL,12,FBut Plaid Cymru has to reach a deal
OL,13,Fwith someone. Right now, it's not at
OL,14,Fall clear who that will be.
OL,26,@qD@VOUrD@HO]
